 We suppose that 
\begin_inset Formula $E$
\end_inset

 is a given set and that, to certain members 
\begin_inset Formula $x\in E$
\end_inset

, we associate a unique object that we shall call 
\begin_inset Formula $p_{x}$
\end_inset

.
